{
  "video_id": "dsMCVMVTdn0",
  "title": "Michael Hansmeyer: Building unimaginable shapes",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Morton Bast Reviewer: Thu-Huong Ha"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15730.0,
      "end_time": 18179.0,
      "text": "As an architect, I often ask myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18179.0,
      "end_time": 21190.0,
      "text": "what is the origin of the forms that we design?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21190.0,
      "end_time": 23924.0,
      "text": "What kind of forms could we design"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23924.0,
      "end_time": 26747.0,
      "text": "if we wouldn&#39;t work with references anymore?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26747.0,
      "end_time": 30131.0,
      "text": "If we had no bias, if we had no preconceptions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30132.0,
      "end_time": 32339.0,
      "text": "what kind of forms could we design"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32339.0,
      "end_time": 33939.0,
      "text": "if we could free ourselves from"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33939.0,
      "end_time": 36750.0,
      "text": "our experience?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36750.0,
      "end_time": 40809.0,
      "text": "If we could free ourselves from our education?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40809.0,
      "end_time": 43836.0,
      "text": "What would these unseen forms look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43836.0,
      "end_time": 47547.0,
      "text": "Would they surprise us? Would they intrigue us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47547.0,
      "end_time": 49961.0,
      "text": "Would they delight us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49962.0,
      "end_time": 53883.0,
      "text": "If so, then how can we go about creating something that is truly new?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53883.0,
      "end_time": 56275.0,
      "text": "I propose we look to nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56275.0,
      "end_time": 60539.0,
      "text": "Nature has been called the greatest architect of forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60539.0,
      "end_time": 64126.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m not saying that we should copy nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64126.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66506.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not saying we should mimic biology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66507.0,
      "end_time": 69955.0,
      "text": "instead I propose that we can borrow nature&#39;s processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69955.0,
      "end_time": 74408.0,
      "text": "We can abstract them and to create something that is new."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74409.0,
      "end_time": 78287.0,
      "text": "Nature&#39;s main process of creation, morphogenesis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78287.0,
      "end_time": 82116.0,
      "text": "is the splitting of one cell into two cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82116.0,
      "end_time": 84173.0,
      "text": "And these cells can either be identical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84173.0,
      "end_time": 86348.0,
      "text": "or they can be distinct from each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86348.0,
      "end_time": 88412.0,
      "text": "through asymmetric cell division."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88412.0,
      "end_time": 92211.0,
      "text": "If we abstract this process, and simplify it as much as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92211.0,
      "end_time": 94444.0,
      "text": "then we could start with a single sheet of paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94444.0,
      "end_time": 96940.0,
      "text": "one surface, and we could make a fold"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96940.0,
      "end_time": 99876.0,
      "text": "and divide the surface into two surfaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99876.0,
      "end_time": 102139.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re free to choose where we make the fold."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102139.0,
      "end_time": 107480.0,
      "text": "And by doing so, we can differentiate the surfaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107490.0,
      "end_time": 108943.0,
      "text": "Through this very simple process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108943.0,
      "end_time": 112554.0,
      "text": "we can create an astounding variety of forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112555.0,
      "end_time": 115280.0,
      "text": "Now, we can take this form and use the same process"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115280.0,
      "end_time": 117272.0,
      "text": "to generate three-dimensional structures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 117272.0,
      "end_time": 119680.0,
      "text": "but rather than folding things by hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 119680.0,
      "end_time": 122265.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll bring the structure into the computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122265.0,
      "end_time": 125240.0,
      "text": "and code it as an algorithm."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125240.0,
      "end_time": 128247.0,
      "text": "And in doing so, we can suddenly fold anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128247.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130406.00000000001,
      "text": "We can fold a million times faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130407.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133568.0,
      "text": "we can fold in hundreds and hundreds of variations."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133568.0,
      "end_time": 136480.0,
      "text": "And as we&#39;re seeking to make something three-dimensional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136480.0,
      "end_time": 139264.0,
      "text": "we start not with a single surface, but with a volume."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139264.0,
      "end_time": 140617.0,
      "text": "A simple volume, the cube."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 140617.0,
      "end_time": 142337.0,
      "text": "If we take its surfaces and fold them"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 142337.0,
      "end_time": 144393.0,
      "text": "again and again and again and again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 144393.0,
      "end_time": 147256.0,
      "text": "then after 16 iterations, 16 steps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 147256.0,
      "end_time": 151105.0,
      "text": "we end up with 400,000 surfaces and a shape that looks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 151105.0,
      "end_time": 153640.0,
      "text": "for instance, like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153640.0,
      "end_time": 156351.0,
      "text": "And if we change where we make the folds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 156352.0,
      "end_time": 157993.0,
      "text": "if we change the folding ratio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 157993.0,
      "end_time": 161416.0,
      "text": "then this cube turns into this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 161416.0,
      "end_time": 165555.0,
      "text": "We can change the folding ratio again to produce this shape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 165555.0,
      "end_time": 167382.0,
      "text": "or this shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 167382.0,
      "end_time": 169500.0,
      "text": "So we exert control over the form"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 169500.0,
      "end_time": 172509.0,
      "text": "by specifying the position of where we&#39;re making the fold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 172509.0,
      "end_time": 177214.0,
      "text": "but essentially you&#39;re looking at a folded cube."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 177215.0,
      "end_time": 178279.0,
      "text": "And we can play with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 178279.0,
      "end_time": 180895.0,
      "text": "We can apply different folding ratios to different parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180895.0,
      "end_time": 183640.0,
      "text": "of the form to create local conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 183640.0,
      "end_time": 185583.0,
      "text": "We can begin to sculpt the form."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 185583.0,
      "end_time": 188471.0,
      "text": "And because we&#39;re doing the folding on the computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 188471.0,
      "end_time": 192167.0,
      "text": "we are completely free of any physical constraints."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 192167.0,
      "end_time": 195118.0,
      "text": "So that means that surfaces can intersect themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 195118.0,
      "end_time": 196607.0,
      "text": "they can become impossibly small."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196607.0,
      "end_time": 200208.0,
      "text": "We can make folds that we otherwise could not make."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 200208.0,
      "end_time": 202850.0,
      "text": "Surfaces can become porous."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 202860.0,
      "end_time": 204815.0,
      "text": "They can stretch. They can tear."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 204815.0,
      "end_time": 209450.0,
      "text": "And all of this expounds the scope of forms that we can produce."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 209450.0,
      "end_time": 212200.0,
      "text": "But in each case, I didn&#39;t design the form."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212200.0,
      "end_time": 216801.0,
      "text": "I designed the process that generated the form."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 216801.0,
      "end_time": 221289.0,
      "text": "In general, if we make a small change to the folding ratio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 221289.0,
      "end_time": 222884.0,
      "text": "which is what you&#39;re seeing here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222884.0,
      "end_time": 226656.0,
      "text": "then the form changes correspondingly."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 226657.0,
      "end_time": 228913.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s only half of the story --"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 228913.0,
      "end_time": 233236.0,
      "text": "99.9 percent of the folding ratios produce not this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 233236.0,
      "end_time": 238131.0,
      "text": "but this, the geometric equivalent of noise."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 238132.0,
      "end_time": 240252.0,
      "text": "The forms that I showed before were made actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 240252.0,
      "end_time": 241900.0,
      "text": "through very long trial and error."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 241900.0,
      "end_time": 245116.0,
      "text": "A far more effective way to create forms, I have found,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 245116.0,
      "end_time": 249400.0,
      "text": "is to use information that is already contained in forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 249400.0,
      "end_time": 251659.0,
      "text": "A very simple form such as this one actually contains"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 251659.0,
      "end_time": 255251.0,
      "text": "a lot of information that may not be visible to the human eye."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 255251.0,
      "end_time": 257732.0,
      "text": "So, for instance, we can plot the length of the edges."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 257732.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261680.00000000003,
      "text": "White surfaces have long edges, black ones have short ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 261670.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264645.0,
      "text": "We can plot the planarity of the surfaces, their curvature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 264645.0,
      "end_time": 268732.0,
      "text": "how radial they are -- all information that may not be"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 268732.0,
      "end_time": 270679.0,
      "text": "instantly visible to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 270679.0,
      "end_time": 273104.0,
      "text": "but that we can bring out, that we can articulate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 273104.0,
      "end_time": 276479.0,
      "text": "and that we can use to control the folding."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 276480.0,
      "end_time": 278439.0,
      "text": "So now I&#39;m not specifying a single"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 278439.0,
      "end_time": 280615.0,
      "text": "ratio anymore to fold it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 280615.0,
      "end_time": 283167.0,
      "text": "but instead I&#39;m establishing a rule,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 283167.0,
      "end_time": 285602.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m establishing a link between a property of a surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 285603.0,
      "end_time": 288576.0,
      "text": "and how that surface is folded."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 288576.0,
      "end_time": 291527.0,
      "text": "And because I&#39;ve designed the process and not the form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 291527.0,
      "end_time": 293849.0,
      "text": "I can run the process again and again and again"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 293849.0,
      "end_time": 296384.0,
      "text": "to produce a whole family of forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 308645.0,
      "end_time": 313870.0,
      "text": "These forms look elaborate, but the process is a very minimal one."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 313880.0,
      "end_time": 314217.0,
      "text": "There is a simple input,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 314217.0,
      "end_time": 316169.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s always a cube that I start with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 316169.0,
      "end_time": 319745.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a very simple operation -- it&#39;s making a fold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 319745.0,
      "end_time": 323697.0,
      "text": "and doing this over and over again."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 323697.0,
      "end_time": 325977.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s bring this process to architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 325977.0,
      "end_time": 327577.0,
      "text": "How? And at what scale?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 327577.0,
      "end_time": 329305.0,
      "text": "I chose to design a column."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 329305.0,
      "end_time": 332681.0,
      "text": "Columns are architectural archetypes."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 332681.0,
      "end_time": 335748.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been used throughout history to express ideals"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 335748.0,
      "end_time": 340823.0,
      "text": "about beauty, about technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 340823.0,
      "end_time": 342745.0,
      "text": "A challenge to me was how we could express"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 342745.0,
      "end_time": 346410.0,
      "text": "this new algorithmic order in a column."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 346410.0,
      "end_time": 349250.0,
      "text": "I started using four cylinders."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 349250.0,
      "end_time": 352801.0,
      "text": "Through a lot of experimentation, these cylinders"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 352801.0,
      "end_time": 355936.0,
      "text": "eventually evolved into this."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 355936.0,
      "end_time": 360551.0,
      "text": "And these columns, they have information at very many scales."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 360552.0,
      "end_time": 363700.0,
      "text": "We can begin to zoom into them."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 363700.0,
      "end_time": 366625.0,
      "text": "The closer one gets, the more new features one discovers."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 366625.0,
      "end_time": 370297.0,
      "text": "Some formations are almost at the threshold of human visibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 370297.0,
      "end_time": 372249.0,
      "text": "And unlike traditional architecture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 372249.0,
      "end_time": 375330.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a single process that creates both the overall form"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 375330.0,
      "end_time": 380378.0,
      "text": "and the microscopic surface detail."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 380378.0,
      "end_time": 383680.0,
      "text": "These forms are undrawable."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 383690.0,
      "end_time": 386445.0,
      "text": "An architect who&#39;s drawing them with a pen and a paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 386445.0,
      "end_time": 388236.0,
      "text": "would probably take months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 388237.0,
      "end_time": 390621.0,
      "text": "or it would take even a year to draw all the sections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 390621.0,
      "end_time": 392924.0,
      "text": "all of the elevations, you can only create something like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 392925.0,
      "end_time": 395610.0,
      "text": "through an algorithm."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 395610.0,
      "end_time": 397920.0,
      "text": "The more interesting question, perhaps, is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 397930.0,
      "end_time": 399722.0,
      "text": "are these forms imaginable?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 399722.0,
      "end_time": 402357.0,
      "text": "Usually, an architect can somehow envision the end state"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 402357.0,
      "end_time": 404221.0,
      "text": "of what he is designing."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 404221.0,
      "end_time": 407460.0,
      "text": "In this case, the process is deterministic."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 407460.0,
      "end_time": 409405.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no randomness involved at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 409405.0,
      "end_time": 411412.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not entirely predictable."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 411412.0,
      "end_time": 412988.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s too many surfaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 412988.0,
      "end_time": 416598.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s too much detail, one can&#39;t see the end state."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 416598.0,
      "end_time": 419812.0,
      "text": "So this leads to a new role for the architect."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 419812.0,
      "end_time": 423423.0,
      "text": "One needs a new method to explore all of the possibilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 423423.0,
      "end_time": 425199.0,
      "text": "that are out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 425199.0,
      "end_time": 428431.0,
      "text": "For one thing, one can design many variants of a form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 428431.0,
      "end_time": 430645.0,
      "text": "in parallel, and one can cultivate them."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 430645.0,
      "end_time": 432893.0,
      "text": "And to go back to the analogy with nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 432893.0,
      "end_time": 435388.0,
      "text": "one can begin to think in terms of populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 435389.0,
      "end_time": 438917.0,
      "text": "one can talk about permutations, about generations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 438917.0,
      "end_time": 443780.0,
      "text": "about crossing and breeding to come up with a design."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 443780.0,
      "end_time": 446164.0,
      "text": "And the architect is really, he moves into the position"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 446165.0,
      "end_time": 449597.0,
      "text": "of being an orchestrator of all of these processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 449597.0,
      "end_time": 451941.0,
      "text": "But enough of the theory."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 451941.0,
      "end_time": 454467.0,
      "text": "At one point I simply wanted to jump inside"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 454468.0,
      "end_time": 458297.0,
      "text": "this image, so to say, I bought these red and blue"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 458297.0,
      "end_time": 461233.0,
      "text": "3D glasses, got up very close to the screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 461233.0,
      "end_time": 463305.0,
      "text": "but still that wasn&#39;t the same as being able to"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 463305.0,
      "end_time": 465657.0,
      "text": "walk around and touch things."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 465657.0,
      "end_time": 467560.0,
      "text": "So there was only one possibility --"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 467560.0,
      "end_time": 470657.0,
      "text": "to bring the column out of the computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 470657.0,
      "end_time": 473577.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s been a lot of talk now about 3D printing."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 473577.0,
      "end_time": 476536.0,
      "text": "For me, or for my purpose at this moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 476536.0,
      "end_time": 479618.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s still too much of an unfavorable tradeoff"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 479618.0,
      "end_time": 486401.0,
      "text": "between scale, on the one hand, and resolution and speed, on the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 486401.0,
      "end_time": 488658.0,
      "text": "So instead, we decided to take the column,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 488658.0,
      "end_time": 491970.0,
      "text": "and we decided to build it as a layered model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 491970.0,
      "end_time": 495224.0,
      "text": "made out of very many slices, thinly stacked over each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 495225.0,
      "end_time": 497122.0,
      "text": "What you&#39;re looking at here is an X-ray"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 497122.0,
      "end_time": 499897.0,
      "text": "of the column that you just saw, viewed from the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 499897.0,
      "end_time": 501897.0,
      "text": "Unbeknownst to me at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 501897.0,
      "end_time": 504272.0,
      "text": "because we had only seen the outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 504273.0,
      "end_time": 506433.0,
      "text": "the surfaces were continuing to fold themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 506433.0,
      "end_time": 508697.0,
      "text": "to grow on the inside of the column,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 508697.0,
      "end_time": 511243.0,
      "text": "which was quite a surprising discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 511243.0,
      "end_time": 514857.0,
      "text": "From this shape, we calculated a cutting line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 514857.0,
      "end_time": 517881.0,
      "text": "and then we gave this cutting line to a laser cutter"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 517881.0,
      "end_time": 521694.0,
      "text": "to produce -- and you&#39;re seeing a segment of it here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 521695.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526586.0,
      "text": "very many thin slices, individually cut, on top of each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 528740.0,
      "end_time": 531553.0,
      "text": "And this is a photo now, it&#39;s not a rendering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 531553.0,
      "end_time": 533353.0,
      "text": "and the column that we ended up with"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 533353.0,
      "end_time": 536400.0,
      "text": "after a lot of work, ended up looking remarkably like the one"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 536400.0,
      "end_time": 540110.0,
      "text": "that we had designed in the computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 540110.0,
      "end_time": 542231.0,
      "text": "Almost all of the details, almost all of the"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 542231.0,
      "end_time": 545271.0,
      "text": "surface intricacies were preserved."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 547886.0,
      "end_time": 550232.0,
      "text": "But it was very labor intensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 550232.0,
      "end_time": 552632.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a huge disconnect at the moment still"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 552633.0,
      "end_time": 555393.0,
      "text": "between the virtual and the physical."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 555393.0,
      "end_time": 557519.0,
      "text": "It took me several months to design the column,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 557519.0,
      "end_time": 560237.0,
      "text": "but ultimately it takes the computer about 30 seconds"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 560237.0,
      "end_time": 563840.0,
      "text": "to calculate all of the 16 million faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 563850.0,
      "end_time": 565460.0,
      "text": "The physical model, on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 565460.0,
      "end_time": 569254.0,
      "text": "is 2,700 layers, one millimeter thick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 569254.0,
      "end_time": 573401.0,
      "text": "it weighs 700 kilos, it&#39;s made of sheet that can cover"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 573401.0,
      "end_time": 575539.0,
      "text": "this entire auditorium."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 575539.0,
      "end_time": 577627.0,
      "text": "And the cutting path that the laser followed"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 577627.0,
      "end_time": 582743.0,
      "text": "goes from here to the airport and back again."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 582744.0,
      "end_time": 584493.0,
      "text": "But it is increasingly possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 584493.0,
      "end_time": 587104.0,
      "text": "Machines are getting faster, it&#39;s getting less expensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 587104.0,
      "end_time": 589864.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s some promising technological developments"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 589864.0,
      "end_time": 591647.0,
      "text": "just on the horizon."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 591647.0,
      "end_time": 594719.0,
      "text": "These are images from the Gwangju Biennale."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 594719.0,
      "end_time": 598243.0,
      "text": "And in this case, I used ABS plastic to produce the columns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 598243.0,
      "end_time": 600970.0,
      "text": "we used the bigger, faster machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 600970.0,
      "end_time": 603154.0,
      "text": "and they have a steel core inside, so they&#39;re structural,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 603154.0,
      "end_time": 606130.0,
      "text": "they can bear loads for once."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 606130.0,
      "end_time": 608145.0,
      "text": "Each column is effectively a hybrid of two columns."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 608145.0,
      "end_time": 611554.0,
      "text": "You can see a different column in the mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 611554.0,
      "end_time": 613603.0,
      "text": "if there&#39;s a mirror behind the column"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 613604.0,
      "end_time": 616676.0,
      "text": "that creates a sort of an optical illusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 616691.0,
      "end_time": 618522.0,
      "text": "So where does this leave us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 618522.0,
      "end_time": 622990.0,
      "text": "I think this project gives us a glimpse of the unseen objects that await us"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 622990.0,
      "end_time": 626873.0,
      "text": "if we as architects begin to think about designing not the object,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 626873.0,
      "end_time": 630266.0,
      "text": "but a process to generate objects."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 630266.0,
      "end_time": 633539.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve shown one simple process that was inspired by nature;"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 633539.0,
      "end_time": 636387.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s countless other ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 636387.0,
      "end_time": 639834.0,
      "text": "In short, we have no constraints."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 639834.0,
      "end_time": 643404.0,
      "text": "Instead, we have processes in our hands right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 643404.0,
      "end_time": 647985.0,
      "text": "that allow us to create structures at all scales"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 647985.0,
      "end_time": 651170.0,
      "text": "that we couldn&#39;t even have dreamt up."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 651170.0,
      "end_time": 655836.0,
      "text": "And, if I may add, at one point we will build them."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 655836.0,
      "end_time": 662459.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}